				<td colspan="2"><span>OK, OK the easiest fix is make the dam songs range 20 so at low levels you can not area...once 65 and you have your wits about the class...and played it more than 1 weekend...you do your aa get extended notes and bingo now you have the same as now.  30 to 35 range which takes a bunch of talent to do in some zones..at least manual kites.
<br />

