Best of both worlds.  It alows seasoned bards to get the needed aa for an otherwise gimp class, and it stops the yaho's from getting to 65 terrorizing zones and giving our class a mud reputation. aka caster wants a mana batery lamer to 2 box....or whatever else.
<br />

